    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贫民窟居民》是一款身临其境的物理模拟格斗游戏，玩家可以在游戏中体验成为一名普通贫民窟居民，在恶劣的犯罪环境中努力生存的独特经历，或者成为一名街头斗士，参加现代贫民窟中正在进行的地下残酷比赛的独特经历。游戏采用创新的战斗系统，玩家可以使用鼠标或操纵杆轻松控制角色，在与强大对手的对决中感受每场战斗的激烈和刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/b5a9462753945d649c42aad875ff47b6.poster.avif?t=1768805912\" width=616 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/b5a9462753945d649c42aad875ff47b6.webm?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/b5a9462753945d649c42aad875ff47b6.mp4?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>基于物理的战斗：准备好体验无与伦比的战斗，你的一举一动都至关重要。所有动画和动作都经过精心设计，具有强大的真实感基础。每个角色都有自己独特的属性，包括体重、力量、耐力和敏捷度，这些属性会影响他们的移动、造成伤害和承受打击的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/e0338fea4bea133ec63088c5fa53bb91.poster.avif?t=1768805912\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/e0338fea4bea133ec63088c5fa53bb91.webm?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/e0338fea4bea133ec63088c5fa53bb91.mp4?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>本地多人游戏：像过去一样通过共享屏幕挑战好友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙盒模式：建立自己的关卡和挑战，尽情发挥自己的创造力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种角色和关卡：参加一对一、一对多或多对多的战斗，证明你在贫民窟居民中的统治地位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/bcca2b38a1e628c346c70ed3628b0ed8.poster.avif?t=1768805912\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/bcca2b38a1e628c346c70ed3628b0ed8.webm?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361830/extras/bcca2b38a1e628c346c70ed3628b0ed8.mp4?t=1768805912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
